headline: California wildfire law eases risk, says Morgan Stanley upgrading PG&E
summary: Investing.com -- California’s passage of wildfire legislation has eased short-term financial risks for its utilities, Morgan Stanley said, upgrading PG&E Corp to Equal weight.
